column2: 1. In the last month, how often have you been upset because of something that happened unexpectedly?
column3: 2. In the last month, how often have you felt that you were unable to control the important things in your life?
column4: 3. In the last month, how often have you felt nervous and "stressed"?
column5: 4. In the last month, how often have you felt confident about your ability to handle your personal problems?
column6: 5. In the last month, how often have you felt that things were going your way?
column7: 6. In the last month, how often have you found that you could not cope with all the things that you had to do?
column8: 7. In the last month, how often have you been able to control irritations in your life?
column9: 8. In the last month, how often have you felt that you were on top of things?
column10: 9. In the last month, how often have you been angered because of things that were outside of your control?
column11: 10. In the last month, how often have you felt difficulties were piling up so high that you could not overcome them?
